OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777482354
OL,3,CMan caught flying drone over primary
OL,4,Cschool to follow children avoids jail
OL,6,FA man from Salisbury who was caught
OL,7,Fflying a drone over a primary school
OL,8,Fhas avoided jail.
OL,10,FJeremy Bird, 48, of Coldharbour Lane,
OL,11,Fflew a drone over a school in the
OL,12,Farea, following children on the
OL,13,Fplaying fields on 13 September 2023.
OL,15,FAt around the same time, police
OL,16,Freceived a report from another school
OL,17,Fwithin the Salisbury area reporting
OL,18,Fthat when teachers were taking the
OL,19,Fchildren out to visit a harvest
OL,20,Ffestival, a man was seen recording the
OL,21,Fchildren and trying to chat with them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
