PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777482354
OL,3,CMan caught flying drone over primary
OL,4,Cschool to follow children avoids jail
OL,6,FHe was seen a short time later in a
OL,7,Fvehicle appearing to be taking more
OL,8,Fpictures of the children.
OL,10,FBird was arrested and searches of his
OL,11,Fdevices found a considerable number of
OL,12,Findecent images of unknown children.
OL,14,FHe was jailed for 19 months, suspended
OL,15,Ffor two years, and also made the
OL,16,Fsubject of a 10-year Sexual Harm
OL,17,FPrevention Order (SHPO).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
