PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777482354
OL,3,CMan caught flying drone over primary
OL,4,Cschool to follow children avoids jail
OL,6,FComplex Crime Investigator Debbie
OL,7,FQuayle said: "I'd like to thank the
OL,8,Fschools for reporting Jeremy Bird's
OL,9,Fbehaviour ` without their support we
OL,10,Fwould be unaware of the extent of his
OL,11,Foffending.
OL,13,F"Mr Bird has taken no accountability
OL,14,Ffor his actions and the fear he put
OL,15,Finto the children when flying his
OL,16,Fdrone near to them to film them.
OL,18,F"He has now been sentenced and has
OL,19,Fbeen made the subject of a Sexual Harm
OL,20,FPrevention Order, which places limits
OL,21,Fon his internet use and travel.
OL,26,@oD@NOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
