CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777482354
OL,3,CMan caught flying drone over primary
OL,4,Cschool to follow children avoids jail
OL,6,F"He is also not allowed to own or use
OL,7,Fa drone and must also allow officers
OL,8,Finto his address to do checks.
OL,10,F"I hope this investigation also shows
OL,11,Fthat we will not tolerate any person
OL,12,Fwho uses drones in an inappropriate
OL,13,Fmanner, and they will be brought to
OL,14,Fjustice."
